    <hyper:description xlink:label="here">
      <h:section>
        <h:p>It would be easy to serve as just a repository of information. A few papers, a few links, and the occassional blog entry and then call it a day. But where's the fun in that?</h:p>
        
        <h:p><h:a href="https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Alan_Kay">The best way to predict the future is to invent it.</h:a></h:p>
        
        <h:p>We develop novel, innovative technologies that leverage the power of hyperspaces and these aren't just research demonstrations -- we encourage real people to use these technologies. And of course you'll find our work <h:a href="github-repository.xml">github</h:a>.</h:p>
       </h:section>
    </hyper:description>
    
